text: Wrecksite is a non-profit organization that documents wrecks around the world and is free to use. For more data you need to subscribe. The website is the world largest online wreck database, and has 187,030 wrecks and 164,050 positions, 62,730 images, 2,347 maritime charts, 31,070 ship owners and builders.
